      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIELDS OF COURAGE (4) sat on the pace last time and recorded the second minor placing from as many runs this prep, beaten a head over 1300m here. Overdue for a win and gets chance. KING AKEED (3) returns after a spell of four-and-a-half months. Started the last campaign impressively when in the placings over 1300m at this track. Has found the right race. BRAZEN BON (1) was a near miss fresh after a long break and will strip far fitter. Has a good record course and distance. POLARISING (5) did well to score at this track two runs ago. Not much luck here last time finishing fourth but beaten only half a length after making up late ground. Doesn't have to improve much. MISS BLACK DIAMOND (8) missed the placings two runs back then didn't do any better last start when 7 lengths away in seventh over 1100m at this track. Suitably placed so can turn things around.",
